## 3. Đánh giá Code Chi tiết

### 3.1 Backend — Điểm mạnh ✅

| Tiêu chí | Đánh giá | Chi tiết |
|---|---|---|
| **Kiến trúc** | ⭐⭐⭐⭐ | Clean layered: controller → service → repository. Shared modules (api-contract, common, security-contract) |
| **Auth** | ⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐ | Use-case driven design (LoginUseCase, RegisterUseCase), interface separation (PasswordHasher/PasswordVerifier) |
| **Doctor** | ⭐⭐⭐⭐ | Full CRUD, overlap validation, BOOKED protection, SOAP sanitizer, audit log |
| **Appointment** | ⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐ | Idempotency key, state machine validation, outbox pattern, slot sync |
| **DB Migrations** | ⭐⭐⭐⭐ | Flyway versioned migrations, index strategies, unique constraints |
| **Error Handling** | ⭐⭐⭐⭐ | Centralized ExceptionHandler per service, ErrorCode enum, ApiResponse envelope |
| **Unit Tests** | ⭐⭐⭐⭐ | 10 test files covering core services |
| **Security** | ⭐⭐⭐⭐ | JWT filter per service, InternalServiceToken for inter-service, RBAC |

